Title            : picc
Authors          : Dominik Oepen
Version          : 1.0.0 04 Aug 2009
License          : See file COPYING
Tested Platforms : Linux 2.6 (Debian, Ubuntu, Om 2008)

Welcome to picc. The purpose of picc is to forward APDUs from the OpenPICC 
card to a smartcard reader via the PCSC middleware. You can use this program
in combination with the virtaulPCD and virtual smartcard programs to achieve
communication of the virtual smartcard and a contactless smartcard reader. 

INSTALLATION
------------

See file INSTALL.

